-<span class="diffline">---+cd go</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+go test ./...</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+```</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+## Status</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+This repo is under active development. Some advanced parity edge cases and async behavior are still being iterated.</span>
-<span class="diffline">---+</span>
